headline: 1 Healthcare Stock to Target This Week and 2 We Turn Down
summary: Personal health and wellness is one of the many secular tailwinds for healthcare companies. Shareholders who bet on the industry have been rewarded lately as healthcare stocks have returned 17.2% over the past six months, topping the S&P 500 by 7.1 percentage points.
